#

Air Fryer Loaded Potato Wedges

35 min
$8
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

SnackAppetizer

Tags:

Air FryerSnackComfort Food

Description

Crispy potato wedges loaded with cheese, bacon, and green onions, all made in your air fryer for a quick and delicious snack!

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 2 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • cooked bacon: 1/2 cup chopped
  • green onions: 1/4 cup sliced
  • sour cream: optional for serving
